{"word":"προβαίνω","slug":"προβαίνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>προβαίνω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πρό\">πρό</a>, βαίνω</el> ‘to step’] ‘move forward from a position’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> spatially <b>go ahead/on <a href='B:470 4:21'>Mt 4:21</a>; <a href='B:480 1:19'>Mk 1:19</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> in imagery and in the <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pf.\">pf.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ptc.\">ptc.</a> indicating advancement in years, <b>advance <a href='B:490 1:7'>Lk 1:7</a>, <a href='B:490 1:18'>18</a>; <a href='B:490 2:36'>2:36</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:προαύλιον\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:προβάλλω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}